Where your are writing event?
Either Functional/class compoent.

How to create a class component?

class AddCart{
// class properties(properties and methods)
//class member - declaration is not required

render(){
return JSX;//JSX describe the UI
}
}

-----------------------------------------------------
class compoent
class AddCart extends React.compoent{
// class properties(properties and methods)
//class member - declaration is not required

render(){
//return JSX;//JSX describe the UI
return(
    <React.Fragment>
)
}
}
export default AddCart


React Fragment?
return statement - return JSX, HTML + Javascript : describe the UI.
                 - One statement 
                 If you want multiple elements, we have to React Framment.

return( <> <p> <h1> </h1></p></>);

return( <React.Fragment> 
          <p> 
             
           </p>
           <h1> 
            Welcome to PSA
           </h1>
        </React.Fragment>);

Note: DOM element will not created.

